title: S12 Ep124: The Skies Are Alive Over ECETI Ranch

description:
Jimmy Church has recently returned from a visit to one of the most active paranormal hot spots in the United States, James Gilliland's ECETI Ranch.

Tonight Jimmy shares his own observations and insights on an incredible visit and shares a startling revelation that was caught on film.

www,JimmyChurchRadio.com

See the video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fepbvdws9Xk

PLUS a Theater of The Mind featuring another personal encounter from Darkness Dave.
